result.name: Beacon Cafe

reviews.text:
Hong Kong styled all day breakfast. Nice one
However, the queuing system has a large room for improvement
A small Caf'e but  good quality food. Good service . Price low.

This is a very classic/traditional Hong Kong style restaurant. 
Waiting time for the food is fast.
The taste of the food and drink are the best I have so far in Hong Kong. 
It’s at the corner of intersection, quiet convenient.
Simple Chinese dinner but clean and I like the breakfast sets. I recommend it.

A dinner set at around HK$100. Seats are not spacious but can be rated as above average on a quieter street in Yuen Long. Again, you cannot expect so much in a local café but a meal there can surely fill up your stomach.
